","/#","#","^.MiskaSecret-The_last_daughter_of_Tisereldanour_is_upstairs... ","/#","#","^-5","/#",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.2.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-4","flg":2},{"s":["^SPELL Comprehend_Languages-",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.3.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-5","flg":2},{"s":["^(Put it away.) ","#","^Q","/#",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-2":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.c-2.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^You squint at the faded text. ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^Most of it is mundane. Supply lists. Coordinates. Complaints. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^But at the bottom, something different. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^A passage written in another hand. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^Older. More deliberate. ","#","^int","/#","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.c-2.32.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^(Read the passage.)",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.c-2.32.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":["^The text shifts into formal script. ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^'<i>Dominus noster mox redibit, posteri eius insidiantur.</i>' ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^'<i>Magnus Thesaurus Esuthi intra muros sedis amissae iacet, sub pedibus proditorum.</i>' ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^'<i>Spiritum filii eius primogeniti inveni et cum eo locutus sum.</i>' ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^'<i>Ossa eius captiva in illis arcanis aulis tenentur, praesentia spurcae ducis goblinorum stabilita.</i>' ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^'<i>Quamdiu illa terram illam tenet, divinae reliquiae eius non movebuntur - sed ingressum obsignavi.</i>' ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^'<i>Solum vero sectatori aperietur.</i>' ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^'<i>Ave, Esuthe! Ignis Litus Verrat!</i>' ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^Draconic. Classical Draconic. ","#","^int ","/#","#","^DC13","/#","\n","^But not quite right. ","#","^int ","/#","#","^DC16","/#","\n","^The grammar is slightly off. ","#","^int ","/#","#","^DC18","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^"},{"->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-3":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.c-3.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",[["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.c-3.7.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^S",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.c-3.7.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":2},{"s":["^F",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.c-3.7.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^The translation forms in your mind, from what you remember from your days of Towers courses. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1.understand"},{"->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.c-3.7.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^You recognize it as Draconic. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^But the meaning escapes you. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^The dialect is old. Formal. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^You'd need magic to translate it properly. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^"},{"->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-4":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.c-4.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.2.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^You cast the spell, touching the paper. ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^The words shift in your mind. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^Translating themselves. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1.understand"},{"->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1"},{"#f":5}],"c-5":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-0.repeatIntro.hub.c-5.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.3.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","end",{"->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5,"#n":"hub"}],{"#f":5,"#n":"repeatIntro"}],{"#f":5}],"g-1":[{"->":".^.^.g-0.repeatIntro.hub"},["^'<i>Our master will soon return, his descendants lay in wait.</i>' ","#","^int","/#","\n","^'<i>The great Trove of Esuth sits within the walls of the lost seat, under the feet of the traitors.</i>' ","#","^int","/#","\n","^'<i>I have found and spoken with the spirit of his first-born son.</i>' ","#","^int","/#","\n","^'<i>His bones are caught in those arcane halls, kept stable by the presence of a filthy goblin chieftess.</i>' ","#","^int","/#","\n","^'<i>As long as she holds that ground, his divine remnants will not move - but I have sealed the entrance.</i>' ","#","^int","/#","\n","^'<i>It will only open for a true follower.</i>' ","#","^int","/#","\n","^'<i>Hail, Esuth! May Fire Sweep the Coast!</i>' ","#","^int ","/#","#","^XPGain ","/#","#","^Minor","/#","\n","^A dragon cultist wrote this. ","#","^int ","/#","#","^.CB_PaperUnderstood=1","/#","\n","^Esuth. The ancient red dragon. ","#","^int ","/#","#","^DC15","/#","\n","^Long dead. ","#","^reply ","/#","#","^int","/#","\n","^His followers believe he'll return. ","#","^int ","/#","#","^DC17","/#","\n","^They always do. ","#","^reply ","/#","#","^int","/#","\n","^The Trove of Esuth. A legendary hoard. ","#","^int ","/#","#","^DC16","/#","\n","^These adventurers were hunting for it. ","#","^int ","/#","#","^.CB_RootsDoorShown=1 ","/#","#","^UpdateEntities","/#","\n","^And they failed. Obviously. ","#","^int ","/#","#","^DC12","/#","\n","^The \"sealed entrance\" that only opens for a true follower... ","#","^int ","/#","#","^DC18","/#","\n","^This paper might be the key. ","#","^int ","/#","#","^DC20","/#","\n","^Or at least part of it. ","#","^reply ","/#","#","^int","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1.understand.132.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-6","flg":2},{"s":["^\"Hail, Esuth. May Fire Sweep the Coast.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1.understand.133.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-7","flg":2},{"s":["^Dragon cultists. Always so dramatic.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1.understand.134.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-8","flg":2},{"s":["^The Trove of Esuth... worth investigating.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-6":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1.understand.c-6.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.132.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^You say the words aloud. ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^Nothing happens. ","#","^OBJ","/#","\n","^But you've memorized them now. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^Just in case. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-2"},{"#f":5}],"c-7":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1.understand.c-7.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.133.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Worshipping dead gods tends to make people theatrical. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-2"},{"#f":5}],"c-8":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-1.understand.c-8.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.134.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^If it exists. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^Most dragon hoards are myths. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^But some aren't. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-2"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5,"#n":"understand"}],{"#f":5}],"g-2":[["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-2.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-9","flg":2},{"s":["^E-Interesting.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-9":["ev",{"^->":"CB_Paper.0.g-2.c-9.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-3"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-3":["end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}}